name: Beeps Boops and Cats v1.10
description:
Cats living in a cassette futuristic world, aimlessly floating about. The hums of computer fans, the twinkle of led lights and purr of felines.

_UNT1L…


!!!WARNING!!!

The BEEP BOOP continues to grow in numbers and glitches in their programming are becoming more present.

The MEOW sense a threat. A new pilot cloning program is initiated. In order to level the playing field the MEOW must increase their numbers and adapt the BEEP BOOP hardware to this new batch of (adorable) resistance fighters. 

For now the threat seems quiet but the MEOW must prepare…
